---
// About — Wathiq
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Wathiq Compliance Gateway">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-tech-black/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/20 border border-primary/40 flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">و</span></div>
        <span class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Wathiq</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="bg-tech-black pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white font-onest font-normal mb-8">Wathiq is compliance infrastructure, built for the Kingdom.</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Saudi Arabia has fully digitized its labor and payroll infrastructure under Vision 2030. 
          Every company must satisfy four government systems simultaneously — Qiwa, GOSI, Mudad, 
          and MHRSD — that cross-reference each other continuously. A violation in one cascades 
          into blocks across all others.
        </p>
        <p>
          The consequence of non-compliance is not a letter or a fine. It is an immediate, automated 
          block on the company's commercial registration. Visas cannot be issued. Sponsorships 
          cannot be transferred. Business licenses cannot be renewed. The block happens without 
          warning and without appeal.
        </p>
        <p>
          Wathiq exists as the permanent, always-on compliance infrastructure layer between Saudi 
          companies and Saudi government systems. We validate payroll before it reaches the bank. 
          We track regulatory changes as they happen. We generate cryptographically signed 
          Verification Passports that serve as board-ready compliance evidence.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is not a tool. It is corporate compliance infrastructure.
        </p>
        <div class="text-sm text-charcoal pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
          <p>Founded 2025. Headquartered in Saudi Arabia.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>